  "detailed_description": "<h1>JOIN OUR DISCORD!</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Where We Are Going, We Don't Need Quarters....</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099910/extras/b24cc2b03c24a4cdfac61b5bc9d2ced1.poster.avif?t=1691391745\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099910/extras/b24cc2b03c24a4cdfac61b5bc9d2ced1.webm?t=1691391745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099910/extras/b24cc2b03c24a4cdfac61b5bc9d2ced1.mp4?t=1691391745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Infinity Pinball is a retro and revolutionary twist on the pinball genre. With nostalgic retro style, and infinitely long procedurally generated pinball tables, the fun never ends!<br><br>Continually flip and ping your ball up up up (and fall down down down) the table levels for endless fun as you earn points, win coins, collect unique balls and unlock new tables.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099910/extras/e45da2018e18c032df78a5bb25246aa1.poster.avif?t=1691391745\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099910/extras/e45da2018e18c032df78a5bb25246aa1.webm?t=1691391745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099910/extras/e45da2018e18c032df78a5bb25246aa1.mp4?t=1691391745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Get your ball into the side pockets to change the bash toy and unlock a bonus stage where even more coins can be won!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099910/extras/735c74fe3dbd13826a851f7d2a676907.poster.avif?t=1691391745\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099910/extras/735c74fe3dbd13826a851f7d2a676907.webm?t=1691391745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099910/extras/735c74fe3dbd13826a851f7d2a676907.mp4?t=1691391745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>5 infinite Pinball Tables, each with its own unique soundtrack, design and bash toys! <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099910/extras/11d3d87a7fe7c2fb41d86cd9724a5251.poster.avif?t=1691391745\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099910/extras/11d3d87a7fe7c2fb41d86cd9724a5251.webm?t=1691391745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099910/extras/11d3d87a7fe7c2fb41d86cd9724a5251.mp4?t=1691391745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>9 Unique Balls to Collect!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099910/extras/6e14ae7a5fcb98c5061ae97f4a6719e8.poster.avif?t=1691391745\" width=450 height=254 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099910/extras/6e14ae7a5fcb98c5061ae97f4a6719e8.webm?t=1691391745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099910/extras/6e14ae7a5fcb98c5061ae97f4a6719e8.mp4?t=1691391745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>11 skins for your virtual Pocket Game!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099910/extras/c17c2e7acef3b81691a925c468da991d.poster.avif?t=1691391745\" width=450 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099910/extras/c17c2e7acef3b81691a925c468da991d.webm?t=1691391745\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2099910/extras/c17c2e7acef3b81691a925c468da991d.mp4?t=1691391745\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
